        fame_level = nil,
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Hieronymus, and you\'ll be forwarded to Adjutant at (J-9).\n2. Talk to Adjutant, and he\'ll ask you for a craft to specialize in.\n3. Once you\'ve picked a craft, he\'ll test you on two synths made with said craft.\n   - What crystal is used for this synth? [List]\n   - What is the first ingredient in this synth? [List]\n   - What is the second ingredient in this synth? [List]\n   - What is the third ingredient in this synth? [List]\n   - What is the fourth ingredient in this synth? [List] (optional)\n   - For example, the items that came up for Cooking were a Herbal Broth, and Roast Mushroom.\n4. Once you\'ve completed your two tests, go back and talk to Hieronymus for your reward.',
