        fame = nil,
        fame_level = nil,
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Hieronymus.\n2. Travel to the Beastmen Ensign at (G-12) in Grauberg.\n   - One can enter solo (very easy at Item Level 119) or use a party.\n3. Once the party leader has selected to enter, you will be transported into Ruhotz Silvermines.\n4. A party of 3 Quadavs, 2 soldiers and 1 caravaneer, will immediately start slowly running towards the exit.\n   - The Caravaneer continues to run to the exit no matter what, the two soldiers will attack your party.\n   - Should the Caravaneer make it to the end of the area, which is quite large, the mission is failed.\n5. Once all three Quadavs are defeated, the Mission Objective is complete.\n6. You must exit the area by using the Twilight Aureola for Hieronymus to acknowledge the mission as successful!\n7. Return and talk to Hieronymus for your reward.',
        notes = '1. There seems to be no time limit to how long you can take to get to Ruhotz Silvermines.\n2. All 3 of the Quadavs are sleepable by Lullaby or the Sleep spells.\n3. Repetitive stun/sleep/bind is helpful in this battle.\n4. The Quadavs are very weak, only having around 2000 HP.',
