        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'Participate in Campaign Battles in the Northlands.\nEligible zones:\n1. Beaucedine Glacier (S)\n2. Xarcabard (S)\n3. Castle Zvahl Baileys (S)\n4. Zvahl Keep (S)\n5. Throne Room (S)\nA minimum of 5000 EXP must be earned in total across one or more Campaign Battles in order to complete this Op.\nReturn to Rasdinice to complete the Op.',
